Description: This module creates and manages AWS VPC networks, including subnets, Internet Gateways, Network ACLs, and NAT Gateways using Terraform.

## Features
- Create VPC with specified CIDR block
- Create public and private subnets
- Enable/disable DNS hostnames and DNS support
- Configure Internet Gateways
- Configure Network ACLs
- Configure NAT Gateways
- Tag resources
